2. cs.SD (Software Engineering) - The paper proposes a new algorithm for community detection, which can be considered as a software engineering problem.
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses the persistence of nodes in a community, which can be seen as a control problem in systems and control.
4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper discusses various metrics and algorithms for community detection, which can be considered as a data structures and algorithms problem.
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a new algorithm for community detection, which can be seen as a machine learning problem.
